text: Jenny Sjöwall (born 17 August 1971) is a Swedish archer. Sjöwall competed at the 1988 Summer Olympics, the 1992 Summer Olympics and the 1996 Summer Olympics.Jenny SjöwallJenny SJOWALL ==References== Category:1971 births Category:Living people Category:Swedish archers Category:Olympians for Sweden Category:People from Karlstad
